title: Endurance Rice Power Bowl — Long-Run Fuel 1
hydrationTip: Pair with 400–600 ml water to support endurance performance.
method: Cook the chosen carbs according to packet instructions.
Heat olive oil in a large pan.
Cook chicken until browned.
Add vegetables and cook until tender.
Combine with cooked carbs and herbs, then portion into four containers.
swaps: Swap chicken for tofu, turkey or beans.
Use sweet potatoes instead of rice or pasta.
Add extra vegetables for more volume and fibre.
